sequenceDiagram
    participant Dev as Developer
    participant GitHub as GitHub Repository
    participant GHA as GitHub Actions
    participant ECR as AWS ECR
    participant EKS as AWS EKS

    Dev->>GitHub: Push commit to main
    GitHub->>GHA: Trigger CI/CD Pipeline
    
    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over GHA: Continuous Integration
        GHA->>GHA: Run Linters (Flake8, GoVet)
        GHA->>GHA: Run Trivy Security Scan
        GHA->>GHA: Build Docker Images
        GHA->>ECR: Push Immutable Images (sha256)
    end
    
    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over GHA: Continuous Deployment
        GHA->>EKS: Apply Kustomize (Platform Base)
        GHA->>EKS: Helm Upgrade Orders API
        GHA->>EKS: Helm Upgrade Payments API
        GHA->>GHA: Verify Deployment Rollout Status
    end
    
    GHA-->>Dev: Pipeline Success/Failure Notification
